Why aren't you guys brushing your teeth?

496
00:33:12,935 --> 00:33:14,100
Parker, what happened?

497
00:33:14,135 --> 00:33:17,400
Porter pushed me and it fell in!
- He pushed me first!

498
00:33:17,435 --> 00:33:19,600
Can I flush it?

499
00:33:19,635 --> 00:33:21,200
No, I'll fish it out later.

500
00:33:21,235 --> 00:33:25,235
You're off the hook for tonight.
