509
00:33:52,635 --> 00:33:55,300
<i>Hearing the hollowness of her own voice,

510
00:33:55,335 --> 00:33:59,335
<i>Lynette realized that it was time
to get one step ahead.

511
00:34:01,535 --> 00:34:05,535
