I caught Ty going through my purse.

515
00:34:26,435 --> 00:34:30,300
Hard bacon have you got.
Was he looking for real money?

516
00:34:30,335 --> 00:34:32,900
Who knows at this point.

517
00:34:32,935 --> 00:34:36,700
Anyway, I knocked a couple back
and things got heated,

518
00:34:36,735 --> 00:34:40,700
pretty soon we're both screaming,
throwing stuff around the apartment--

519
00:34:40,735 --> 00:34:43,500
Next thing you know, the lady upstairs
calls the cops on us.

520
00:34:43,535 --> 00:34:47,535
Aw, gimme a break.

521
00:34:49,035 --> 00:34:53,035
