trying to tell me how to raise my boy.

522
00:34:55,635 --> 00:34:59,635
Kids. If I knew then what I know now,
I'd have had that hysterectomy 20 years ago.

523
00:35:12,235 --> 00:35:14,800
Bree--
- Don't get up. I'll be quick.

524
00:35:14,835 --> 00:35:18,835
Andrew. All any parent can do is try to provide
their child with the tools to succeed in life.

525
00:35:20,835 --> 00:35:24,100
Education, love, a good clean safe home.

526
00:35:24,135 --> 00:35:27,300
I have given you those things,
and I am through feeling guilty.

527
00:35:27,335 --> 00:35:30,500
So if you want to piss your life away
and blame it on how horrible things are, go ahead.

528
00:35:30,535 --> 00:35:34,535
But I want it stated for the record
that I am a good mother.

529
00:35:34,635 --> 00:35:38,635
Did you hear me?
I -- am a good -- mother.

530
00:35:40,535 --> 00:35:43,300
Bree.

531
00:35:43,335 --> 00:35:45,600
Andrew just told me
he thinks

532
00:35:45,635 --> 00:35:49,300
he might be gay.

533
00:35:49,335 --> 00:35:50,034
What?

534
00:35:50,035 --> 00:35:53,000
That's why he wanted me to come in first.

535
00:35:53,035 --> 00:35:57,035
He thought I could take it better.

536
00:36:01,835 --> 00:36:05,835
Well, that's right.
I will be waiting in the car.

537
00:36:13,635 --> 00:36:17,635
Mrs Solís!
Where are you going to?

538
00:36:21,735 --> 00:36:21,934
OK--

539
00:36:21,935 --> 00:36:25,400
Are your roommates here?
- No.

540
00:36:25,435 --> 00:36:28,700
Are you OK?
- Yeah.

541
00:36:28,735 --> 00:36:31,300
What's this?
- That-- uh--

542
00:36:31,335 --> 00:36:33,200
Carlos just got a little rough.

543
00:36:33,235 --> 00:36:34,600
Made me sign some paper.

544
00:36:34,635 --> 00:36:38,635
Did he hurt you?

545
00:36:39,735 --> 00:36:41,200
John, what are you doing?

546
00:36:41,235 --> 00:36:42,200
