554
00:37:18,135 --> 00:37:19,900
Oh Morty, look who's here!

555
00:37:19,935 --> 00:37:22,600
Hey Molly, hi.

556
00:37:22,635 --> 00:37:25,100
Suzie, what brings you here?

557
00:37:25,135 --> 00:37:29,135
Mom.
She's right over there.

558
00:37:29,935 --> 00:37:32,400
What's she doing out there?

559
00:37:32,435 --> 00:37:35,800
