563
00:37:42,535 --> 00:37:44,700
Why was she hitting you?

564
00:37:44,735 --> 00:37:47,400
I threw-- threw a book at her.

565
00:37:47,435 --> 00:37:49,500
Morty!
- It was a paperback!

566
00:37:49,535 --> 00:37:52,900
Even so!
- At least I missed.

567
00:37:52,935 --> 00:37:56,500
And she-- she hit me square in the gut.

568
00:37:56,535 --> 00:38:00,500
Wanna see the bruise?
- That's OK.

569
00:38:00,535 --> 00:38:04,535
It really hurt.
- I understand.

570
00:38:05,035 --> 00:38:09,035
So-- could you just go out
and apologize?

571
00:38:10,235 --> 00:38:12,500
No.
- Why?

572
00:38:12,535 --> 00:38:13,700
'Cause I don't want her back.

573
00:38:13,735 --> 00:38:16,700
Morty?
