584
00:38:51,635 --> 00:38:55,635
It didn't work out.
- I'm sorry.

585
00:38:56,035 --> 00:39:00,035
And she will burn up all my oxygen,
and I need it.

586
00:39:00,735 --> 00:39:02,800
Please, can't you give her another chance?

587
00:39:02,835 --> 00:39:04,800
You guys are really good together.

588
00:39:04,835 --> 00:39:08,700
You know, when--
when there's no violence.

589
00:39:08,735 --> 00:39:12,735
We do have chemistry.
