593
00:39:24,835 --> 00:39:28,835
Now.

594
00:39:29,635 --> 00:39:33,635
OK.

595
00:39:41,435 --> 00:39:43,400
That was a mighty big sigh.

596
00:39:43,435 --> 00:39:46,400
I just keep thinking it's coming nearer
and I can't stop it.   - What?

597
00:39:46,435 --> 00:39:50,435
The day my mother will need to
move in with me, and I won't have a choice.

598
00:39:51,135 --> 00:39:52,700
Mhm.
- You know, it's years away.

599
00:39:52,735 --> 00:39:56,735
She's youthful and vibrant, thank god.
But time flies.

600
00:39:59,335 --> 00:40:01,000
One day, she won't be able to
take care of herself anymore

601
00:40:01,035 --> 00:40:05,035
and I have to step up.
- I suppose that's true.

602
00:40:05,835 --> 00:40:09,835
It's nature's little joke that children
ultimately end up parenting their parents.

603
00:40:12,235 --> 00:40:14,500
When that day comes,
I'll be ready.

604
00:40:14,535 --> 00:40:18,535
Honey, you better get out there.

605
00:40:56,435 --> 00:41:00,435
Hey.

606
00:41:01,435 --> 00:41:05,435
