- Lynette. Don't.

607
00:41:07,635 --> 00:41:11,200
The fact that you just crossed that street
means the world to me.

608
00:41:11,235 --> 00:41:15,000
And if anyone here should apologize,
it's me.

609
00:41:15,035 --> 00:41:19,035
Thank you.

610
00:41:21,935 --> 00:41:25,935
Looks like Tom's got the mob under control.
You want to have some coffee?

611
00:41:26,335 --> 00:41:30,335
Sit around-- bitch about that case--

612
00:41:30,835 --> 00:41:34,835
I would love to.
