613
00:41:39,735 --> 00:41:43,735
<i>Children come into the world
with their own agendas.

614
00:41:44,235 --> 00:41:48,235
<i>Some, to brighten our days.

615
00:41:48,935 --> 00:41:52,935
<i>Some, to test our patience.

616
00:41:55,835 --> 00:41:59,835
<i>Some, to give us purpose.

617
00:42:04,035 --> 00:42:08,035
<i>Some, to take care of us.

618
00:42:11,735 --> 00:42:15,735
<i>Yes, when they come,
children change everything.

619
00:42:25,635 --> 00:42:27,600
<i>Especially
when they're not invited.

